{"tid":2186889,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"元朗14歲中槍男童被控暴動　9．8粉嶺裁判法院提堂","createTime":"2020-09-03T09:30:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T10:02:43.000Z","uid":6497,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1e040ae95e4b19a82c0e967b98ed9cb5be7cf3b5","tid":2186889,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T09:30:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20200903/s00001/4057f37faeb5127c65ca7630ffb30a60.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20200903%2Fs00001%2F4057f37faeb5127c65ca7630ffb30a60.jpg&h=d6a8aaea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200903/s00001/1599124629451/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200903%2Fs00001%2F1599124629451%2F&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hc0BU04RHr%2BP31d0xuhNw0M%3D&h=21466a02\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200903%2Fs00001%2F1599124629451%2F&h=30334301\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200903/s00001/1599124629451/</a><br />\n<br />\n去年10月4日，元朗有便衣警員與示威者衝突，開真槍射中14歲男童的大腿。警方今（3日）表示，該中槍男童將被落案起訴一項暴動罪及一項有意圖造成身體嚴重傷害罪，案件將於下周二（8日）在粉嶺裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n當晚9時許，一名便衣警員駕車經過元朗大馬路時與示威者衝突，其間傳出槍聲，有示威者繼續以雨傘等襲擊他，並投擲燃燒彈，火勢一度燒着警員的衣服，警員匆忙逃出並不斷揈手撲火，混亂間手槍跌在地上，有人上前疑企圖搶槍，警員衝前奪回，但留下彈匣。<br />\n<br />\n警員其後致電求援，此時他第二次被擲燃燒彈，衣服一度再次着火。事件中一名14歲男童左大腿中槍，送往屯門醫院接受手術治療。"},{"pid":"b3e3c22187a10f58d5e68b983b2ab2ad568ee5e5","tid":2186889,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T09:31:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nVzd6Mt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnVzd6Mt.jpg&h=f7cd83b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aded9fc737eb691179b3b379bd1b3ae1880e7b2b","tid":2186889,"uid":13065,"like":2,"dislike":0,"sc